754
00:43:29,089 --> 00:43:31,489
Does she really want to inform you?

755
00:43:31,490 --> 00:43:32,490
Let her be this time.

756
00:43:33,609 --> 00:43:37,650
Mu Jin, do not tell her
about my military expedition.

